request.description:
### List Setting Groups
Retrieve a list of all setting groups.

#### Example Response
```json
{
  "data": [
    {
      "name": "general",
      "label": "General",
      "icon": "settings",
      "description": "General store settings",
      "settings_count": 5
    },
    {
      "name": "payment",
      "label": "Payments",
      "icon": "credit-card",
      "description": "Payment gateway settings",
      "settings_count": 8
    }
  ]
}
```
